																				courage and capability to spot changes in the
																				circumstances, make more assumptions, get them right
																				or wrong and make corrections on the
																				course.&nbsp;Meanwhile please note, we don't want
																				you to&nbsp;over react with your financial plan
																				now.&nbsp;Hang in there.&nbsp;But regularly
																				review&nbsp;your financial plan and
																				rebalance&nbsp;your portfolio every year.
																				That&nbsp;is mandatory.</td>
